    Line up help. You need more than just yourself to get the word out. Get your collaborators, peers, and cast and crew involved.<br><br>

    Summarize your story and turn it into an awesome press release. Research journalists and send your press release to the appropriate ones. <%= link_to "Tips for press releases", 'https://chuffed.org/academy/articles/detail/5-steps-to-get-pr', :target => "_blank" %><br><br>

  <% end %>  

